title: [Mist Harbor, Vineyard]
description: Cream-hued limestone walls glimmer in the golden sunlight, the new mortar that surrounds them dark against their incandescent coloring.  A carved limestone staircase rises from the crushed cinnamon bark path that winds its way to the north east and provide egress to the top of the guild.
